        h1 Bruno Pazzim
        p
          | Hey there! This is the personal website of Bruno Pazzim. He is co-founder and CBDO at&nbsp
          a href="http://www.codeland.com.br" target="_blank" CODELAND
          | . Bruno is a fellow Ruby on Rails developer, and although his work doesn't involve so much programming anymore, he still writes some code to this day - he just enjoys it too much to stop. He thinks highly of people who can write well, so he does his own homework in&nbsp
          a href="https://medium.com/@brunopazzim" target="_blank" his blog
          | . He also is a superhero on weekends (
          a href="/img/bruno_onstage.jpg" target="_blank" and I MEAN IT!
