          h2 Co-founder and CBDO at CODELAND
          p
            a href="http://www.codeland.com.br" target="_blank" CODELAND
            | &nbspis an agile web development company, which specialized in releasing new digital businesses through carefully crafted software. They work with worldwide clients to develop businesses for enterpreneurs and big companies who wish to release new services or products. Bruno co-founded the company together with other 3 fine gentleman. Today he works there as a Business Developer to make shit happen.

        img.img src="img/superhero.png"
        h2 Super Hero at weekends
        p
          | Bruno is indeed a creative person. Why else would he be able to make these wicked costumes out of everyday materials? He is a cosplayer - someone who makes costumes to participate in contests in various conventions. He's the Brazillian champion of the&nbsp
          a href="http://www.worldcosplaysummit.jp/en/" target="_blank" World Cosplay Summit
          | , the most important cosplay contest in the world. In 2014 he attended the world finals in Japan, together with 24 other countries. Such honor!

        img.img src="img/wacken.png"
        h2 Metalhead
        p
          | Bruno once had this very long hair, and of course - a band! He played guitars for the Winter Falls, a local melodic metal group of very close friends. Although he isn't part of any band anymore, he went as far as going to the Holy Metal Land in Germany,&nbsp
          a href="http://www.wacken.com/" target="_blank" Wacken Open Air
          | , to see the bands he loves.

